Package: IDmeasurer
Type: Package
Title: Calculates Metrics of Individual Identity in Animal Signals
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: person("Pavel", "Linhart", email = "pavel.linhart@centrum.cz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Pavel Linhart <pavel.linhart@centrum.cz>
Description: 'IDmeasurer' package accompanies the research article reviewing metrics that have been suggested and used to measure indivdual identity in animal signals. It allows calculation of different individual identity metrics and provides a aims to provide common tools for scholars studying individual identity in animal signals.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
